			<div class="postbrown">
				<h2 class="titlebrown">Exotic Fudge Recipes</h2>
								<div class="entry">
<p>
<strong>Join me</strong> in making fudge the old-fashioned way. These easy fudge recipes use traditional ingredients like milk, butter, and sugar (NOT marshmallow cream!).
Every fudge recipe on this site has been personally tried to ensure that soft, creamy, delicious fudge can result.</p>
<p>If you're new to fudge making, I recommend reading the <a href="toolsandtips.php">Tools & Tips</a>. I learned the hard way that making the best fudge is less about
the ingredients and more about the technique.</p>
<p>Give one of these homemade fudge recipes a try. Make grandma proud!</p>
<p>Be sure and visit my other site: <a href="http://englishsconerecipes.blogspot.com/" target="_blank">English Scone Recipes</a>.</p>
<div class="buttonline">
<a href="http://englishsconerecipes.blogspot.com/" target="_blank"><img src="images/englishsconerecipes.png" border=0 alt="English Scone Recipes" title="English Scone Recipes" /></a>
</div>
