		<a class="a2a_dd" href="http://www.addtoany.com/share_save?linkname=&amp;linkurl=http%3A%2F%2Foldtymefudgerecipes.com"><img src="http://static.addtoany.com/buttons/share_save_171_16.png" width="171" height="16" border="0" alt="Share/Bookmark"/></a><script type="text/javascript">a2a_linkurl="http://oldtymefudgerecipes.com";a2a_onclick=1;</script><script type="text/javascript" src="http://static.addtoany.com/menu/page.js"></script>	<p>
